Source code for play event-based webapp at bidsilent.net

A playground for event-based webapps

To use:

1. Clone this repo
2. Install & Start Redis (redis-server)
3. Start EventHub (% npm start EventHub)
4. Start app (% sudo node ./modctl.js start all)  (sudo to listen on port 80)
5. Point browser to http://localhost
6. Profit!
